<br>
&quot;Hello Sal. There's something I need to talk to you about&quot;.<br>
<br>
&quot;What is it Mo&quot;, said Saladin around mouthfulls of hot soup.<br>
<br>
&quot;It's the lady Sampetra. I get weird feelings from her&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;What do you mean, she seemed okay to me. What kind of feelings?&quot;<br>
<br>
Mo took a long swig from his flagon before answering. &quot;Evil feelings&quot;.<br>
<br>
Saladin would've laughed if his mouth wasn't burning from the soup.<br>
<br>
&quot;Bad feelings? What are you talking about. I think that beer is playing tricks on your mind&quot;.<br>
<br>
Mo chuckled. &quot;Could very well be Sal. Maybe all I need is a nap&quot;.<br>
<br>
&quot;Maybe&quot;, said Sal who wanted to be left alone so he can eat in peace.<br>
<br>
