Two students raise their hands. One of them belonged to Janus. Sampetra chose her.<br>
<br>
&quot;Master, they are magic users who have been altered in some way&quot;.<br>
<br>
&quot;Do you have an example young Janus&quot;, asked Sampetra.<br>
<br>
&quot;Some may have a skin alteration that gives their skin a bluish color. Some acquire a glow around them. And others hair moves without any wind. Those are the sure signs of a magic user.<br>
<br>
